name: Moai 5: New Generation - Collector's Edition
summary: Moai V: New Generation Collector's Edition is a strategic time management game that will put the power of the elements at your fingertips. Guide tribal members and draw elemental signs with your mouse cursor as you guide your village to safety. Manage resources, unlock bonus levels, and lead your tribe to victory. Play Moai V: New Generation Collector's Edition today!
